      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. Everything runs smoothly and it's ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
